{"tid":522892,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"峴港五行山騙子","createTime":"2018-01-08T03:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-11T03:57:47.000Z","uid":96406,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1cf18ce1301f9140b5b06dae9a4ed73450629afe","tid":522892,"uid":96406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T03:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/112703_52ec60ddecd5ba71ce2d871404deffce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F112703_52ec60ddecd5ba71ce2d871404deffce.png&h=5cf51dac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/08/112708_9dd0e21538299ed96d297b9239a373ec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F112708_9dd0e21538299ed96d297b9239a373ec.png&h=900700ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去峴港既打打絲打小心五行山下呢間士多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事關VND 面額勁大幾十萬幾百萬咁<br />\n果次我口渴買支水 ， 佢收我30000盾 = HKD 10<br />\n我都知比人搵笨架啦 正當我數緊錢果陣 想拎張100000 比佢找 點知佢扮撚曬野一鳩拎左我張20000  <br />\n我心知不妙先醒起佢拎撚左我張200000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩即刻屌鳩佢先回水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去越南既巴絲真係小心啲遊客區 <br />\n不過總括黎講 峴港真係幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a44f012a35bc6c11bb2fff674b1063e0e8805bd","tid":522892,"uid":96406,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T04:12:56.000Z","msg":"邊個偷偷留下腐皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a259ed0766ebef946f86244c3e86f57f9b6b204","tid":522892,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018